page.title: 07WILD FLOWERS
page.content: This is a list of some of the wild flowers found near Pencerrig School. dandelion buttercup primrose cowslip daisy violet coltsfoot clover vetch cowparsley sunspurge scarlet-pimpernel dogrose fumitory speedwell lady'ssmock honeysuckle stitchwort ragged-robin meadow-sweet garlic-mustard bluebell wild-strawberry celandine snowdrop groundsel willowherb birdsfoottrefoil nettle ox-eye-daisy shepherd's-purse Welsh-poppy charlock St.John'swort pink-campion elder-flower foxgloves ground-elder hawkbit wild-daffodil common-thistle wood-anemone ragwort wood-sorrel deadly-nightshade harebell lords-and-ladies polypody blackberry cut-leaved-cranesbill ground-ivy scabious.The following are UNCOMMON OR RARE: dyersgreenweed zigzag-clover columbine spear-thistle agrimony goats beard polygonum yellow-oat-grass.
